.DT
money
$MUDNAME$ player help
money

.SH Name
.SI 5
money - Show how much cash you are carrying
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
money
money brief
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command shows you how much money you are carrying, including any
you have in open or transparent containers.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> money
Your purse contains 6 electrum coins, 7 silver coins and 6 platinum coins.
Your brown backpack contains 7 electrum coins.
You have a total of 13 electrum coins, 7 silver coins and 6 platinum coins.

> money brief
You have a total of 6 platinum coins.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
currency
.EP
